{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u490e15de\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">检测模块之间的循环依赖，主要可以通过 Webpack 插件、ESLint 规则和可视化工具三种方式来实现。下面为你详细介绍这几种主流方案。</span></p><h3 id=\"vglkn\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🛠️</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 核心方案：使用 Webpack 插件</span></h3><p id=\"u3c578a74\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在 Webpack 构建流程中直接检测和报告循环依赖，是最常用和自动化程度最高的方法。</span></p><h4 id=\"BeRll\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code></h4><p id=\"u8f0f9045\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这是最主流的 Webpack 循环依赖检测插件，每周下载量超过百万，稳定性高。它能在编译时分析模块依赖图，并准确定位循环链路。</span></p><p id=\"u93c11c27\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">安装与基础配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"JROTR\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code>npm install --save-dev circular-dependency-plugin</code></pre><p id=\"u770814c5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中引入并配置：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"uWEBh\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>const CircularDependencyPlugin = require('circular-dependency-plugin')\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  // ... 其他配置\n  plugins: [\n    new CircularDependencyPlugin({\n      // 排除 node_modules 下的文件\n      exclude: /node_modules/,\n      // 设置为 true 则将循环依赖视为错误，导致构建失败；false 则仅输出警告\n      failOnError: false,\n      // 允许包含异步导入的循环，例如通过 import() 引入\n      allowAsyncCycles: false,\n      // 设置当前工作目录，用于显示模块路径\n      cwd: process.cwd(),\n    })\n  ]\n}</code></pre><p id=\"u0f518fc6\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">进阶用法</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">onDetected</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 钩子，你可以自定义处理逻辑，比如收集所有循环路径并在构建结束时统计数量：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"x8CUC\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>new CircularDependencyPlugin({\n  onDetected({ module: webpackModuleRecord, paths, compilation }) {\n    // paths 是一个包含循环依赖路径的数组，例如 ['a.js', 'b.js', 'a.js']\n    compilation.warnings.push(new Error(paths.join(' -&gt; ')))\n  },\n})</code></pre><h3 id=\"KHjdh\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🔍</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 辅助方案：ESLint 静态检查</span></h3><p id=\"u5ef77fd4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果你希望在编写代码的阶段就能发现循环依赖，可以使用 ESLint 规则。</span></p><h4 id=\"LU7ML\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则</span></h4><p id=\"u258c5d2b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 插件提供的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则，可以在不运行构建的情况下，静态分析代码中的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 语句来检测循环依赖。</span></p><p id=\"u282a5653\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">配置方法</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"json\" id=\"yNma3\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-json\"><code>{\n  &quot;plugins&quot;: [&quot;import&quot;],\n  &quot;rules&quot;: {\n    &quot;import/no-cycle&quot;: [&quot;error&quot;, { &quot;maxDepth&quot;: 10 }]\n  }\n}</code></pre><p id=\"u7d2b732e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这种方式可以让你在开发时实时得到反馈，但它的分析深度和准确性不如在完整构建流程中的 Webpack 插件。</span></p><h3 id=\"GZWfJ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">📊</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 可视化工具：深入理解依赖关系</span></h3><p id=\"uc6345ed9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当项目复杂时，仅仅知道有循环依赖可能还不够，需要直观地看到依赖关系图来帮助重构。</span></p><h4 id=\"fzgVy\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependency-cruiser</span></code></h4><p id=\"u08bf8f98\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 是一个强大的依赖关系分析和可视化工具，可以生成整个项目的依赖关系图，清晰地展示模块间的所有联系，包括循环依赖。</span></p><p id=\"u06053eee\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">基本使用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"ICdHP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code># 安装\nnpm install --save-dev dependency-cruiser\n\n# 生成依赖图 (SVG 格式)\nnpx depcruise src --include-only &quot;^src&quot; --output-type dot | dot -T svg &gt; dependency-graph.svg</code></pre><h4 id=\"Etujd\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code></h4><p id=\"u5c80da28\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这个工具可以配合 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 使用，将检测到的循环依赖生成一个交互式的 HTML 可视化页面。页面中，你可以看到每个循环链路的详细路径，节点颜色代表不同目录，动画箭头指示了依赖方向。</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"clNbX\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// webpack.config.js\nconst CircularDependencyPlugin = require('circular-dependency-plugin');\nconst visualizer = require('circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer');\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [\n    new CircularDependencyPlugin(visualizer({\n      exclude: /node_modules/,\n    }, {\n      // 指定输出 HTML 文件的路径\n      filepath: path.join(__dirname, 'circular-deps.html')\n    }))\n  ]\n};</code></pre><h3 id=\"DHvK8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">💡</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 总结与建议</span></h3><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u079042d3\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">日常开发首选</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中引入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，并将其 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">failOnError</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 设置为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 作为警告，避免打断开发流程，但能时刻提醒你关注。</span></li><li id=\"ub1f6846c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">代码提交前检查</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在 CI/CD 流程或 Git 钩子中，可以运行一个专门的 Webpack 构建，将 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">failOnError</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 设为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，确保任何引入新循环依赖的代码都无法合入。</span></li><li id=\"u2f7677c6\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">复杂问题定位</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：当出现难以理解的循环依赖时，使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 生成依赖图，直观地分析模块结构。</span></li><li id=\"u3c71ca8d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">规范前置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：结合 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">ESLint</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，在编码阶段就给开发者最快速的提示。</span></li></ol></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u490e15de\" id=\"u490e15de\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5ecaf541\" id=\"u5ecaf541\">检测模块之间的循环依赖，主要可以通过 Webpack 插件、ESLint 规则和可视化工具三种方式来实现。下面为你详细介绍这几种主流方案。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"vglkn\" id=\"vglkn\"><span data-lake-id=\"u346c7c84\" id=\"u346c7c84\">🛠️</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc7566720\" id=\"uc7566720\"> 核心方案：使用 Webpack 插件</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u3c578a74\" id=\"u3c578a74\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub220080d\" id=\"ub220080d\">在 Webpack 构建流程中直接检测和报告循环依赖，是最常用和自动化程度最高的方法。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"BeRll\" id=\"BeRll\"><code data-lake-id=\"ua1810ddd\" id=\"ua1810ddd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u944ea346\" id=\"u944ea346\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u8f0f9045\" id=\"u8f0f9045\"><span data-lake-id=\"u501b6ce5\" id=\"u501b6ce5\">这是最主流的 Webpack 循环依赖检测插件，每周下载量超过百万，稳定性高。它能在编译时分析模块依赖图，并准确定位循环链路。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u93c11c27\" id=\"u93c11c27\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf128ee23\" id=\"uf128ee23\">安装与基础配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u743f0c94\" id=\"u743f0c94\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22npm%20install%20--save-dev%20circular-dependency-plugin%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22JROTR%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u770814c5\" id=\"u770814c5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5240c42e\" id=\"u5240c42e\">在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3ebfe6de\" id=\"u3ebfe6de\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27a76e2a\" id=\"u27a76e2a\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7237a637\" id=\"u7237a637\"> 中引入并配置：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20CircularDependencyPlugin%20%3D%20require('circular-dependency-plugin')%5Cn%5Cnmodule.exports%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%2F%2F%20...%20%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%5Cn%20%20plugins%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20new%20CircularDependencyPlugin(%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%20node_modules%20%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20exclude%3A%20%2Fnode_modules%2F%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA%20true%20%E5%88%99%E5%B0%86%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E8%A7%86%E4%B8%BA%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%EF%BC%9Bfalse%20%E5%88%99%E4%BB%85%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20failOnError%3A%20false%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%20import()%20%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20allowAsyncCycles%3A%20false%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20cwd%3A%20process.cwd()%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D)%5Cn%20%20%5D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22uWEBh%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u0f518fc6\" id=\"u0f518fc6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u13990860\" id=\"u13990860\">进阶用法</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3af10ac4\" id=\"u3af10ac4\">：通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u95826e35\" id=\"u95826e35\"><span data-lake-id=\"u068d9c3a\" id=\"u068d9c3a\">onDetected</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3da17c1d\" id=\"u3da17c1d\"> 钩子，你可以自定义处理逻辑，比如收集所有循环路径并在构建结束时统计数量：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22new%20CircularDependencyPlugin(%7B%5Cn%20%20onDetected(%7B%20module%3A%20webpackModuleRecord%2C%20paths%2C%20compilation%20%7D)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20paths%20%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%20%5B'a.js'%2C%20'b.js'%2C%20'a.js'%5D%5Cn%20%20%20%20compilation.warnings.push(new%20Error(paths.join('%20-%3E%20')))%5Cn%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22x8CUC%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"KHjdh\" id=\"KHjdh\"><span data-lake-id=\"uff312419\" id=\"uff312419\">🔍</span><span data-lake-id=\"u06c1e3e9\" id=\"u06c1e3e9\"> 辅助方案：ESLint 静态检查</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u5ef77fd4\" id=\"u5ef77fd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1c0e7753\" id=\"u1c0e7753\">如果你希望在编写代码的阶段就能发现循环依赖，可以使用 ESLint 规则。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"LU7ML\" id=\"LU7ML\"><code data-lake-id=\"u49fa1b72\" id=\"u49fa1b72\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4068a601\" id=\"u4068a601\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uecc8ca56\" id=\"uecc8ca56\"> 规则</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u258c5d2b\" id=\"u258c5d2b\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufd19a840\" id=\"ufd19a840\">通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufeea798b\" id=\"ufeea798b\"><span data-lake-id=\"udc84f058\" id=\"udc84f058\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udb767fbf\" id=\"udb767fbf\"> 插件提供的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf1d2616a\" id=\"uf1d2616a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u03b43b8a\" id=\"u03b43b8a\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u03947040\" id=\"u03947040\"> 规则，可以在不运行构建的情况下，静态分析代码中的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud96cf7d1\" id=\"ud96cf7d1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u92158cd8\" id=\"u92158cd8\">import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u43a8242a\" id=\"u43a8242a\"> 语句来检测循环依赖。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u282a5653\" id=\"u282a5653\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u080b39e4\" id=\"u080b39e4\">配置方法</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u23681dd9\" id=\"u23681dd9\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22json%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%7B%5Cn%20%20%5C%22plugins%5C%22%3A%20%5B%5C%22import%5C%22%5D%2C%5Cn%20%20%5C%22rules%5C%22%3A%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5C%22import%2Fno-cycle%5C%22%3A%20%5B%5C%22error%5C%22%2C%20%7B%20%5C%22maxDepth%5C%22%3A%2010%20%7D%5D%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22yNma3%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u7d2b732e\" id=\"u7d2b732e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc391d93\" id=\"ufc391d93\">这种方式可以让你在开发时实时得到反馈，但它的分析深度和准确性不如在完整构建流程中的 Webpack 插件。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"GZWfJ\" id=\"GZWfJ\"><span data-lake-id=\"uddd27698\" id=\"uddd27698\">📊</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc119ca2c\" id=\"uc119ca2c\"> 可视化工具：深入理解依赖关系</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc6345ed9\" id=\"uc6345ed9\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf4a70df0\" id=\"uf4a70df0\">当项目复杂时，仅仅知道有循环依赖可能还不够，需要直观地看到依赖关系图来帮助重构。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"fzgVy\" id=\"fzgVy\"><code data-lake-id=\"u96691362\" id=\"u96691362\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub4040051\" id=\"ub4040051\">dependency-cruiser</span></code></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u08bf8f98\" id=\"u08bf8f98\"><code data-lake-id=\"u814c1a53\" id=\"u814c1a53\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8e492ef5\" id=\"u8e492ef5\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u29f514dc\" id=\"u29f514dc\"> 是一个强大的依赖关系分析和可视化工具，可以生成整个项目的依赖关系图，清晰地展示模块间的所有联系，包括循环依赖。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u06053eee\" id=\"u06053eee\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u61e4022a\" id=\"u61e4022a\">基本使用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua07a563e\" id=\"ua07a563e\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%5Cnnpm%20install%20--save-dev%20dependency-cruiser%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E5%9B%BE%20(SVG%20%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F)%5Cnnpx%20depcruise%20src%20--include-only%20%5C%22%5Esrc%5C%22%20--output-type%20dot%20%7C%20dot%20-T%20svg%20%3E%20dependency-graph.svg%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22ICdHP%22%7D\"></card><h4 data-lake-id=\"Etujd\" id=\"Etujd\"><code data-lake-id=\"ub81511eb\" id=\"ub81511eb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a8a5516\" id=\"u3a8a5516\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u5c80da28\" id=\"u5c80da28\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a15cf0c\" id=\"u7a15cf0c\">这个工具可以配合 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1aa18db\" id=\"ua1aa18db\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud08fa4bf\" id=\"ud08fa4bf\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3d633b0d\" id=\"u3d633b0d\"> 使用，将检测到的循环依赖生成一个交互式的 HTML 可视化页面。页面中，你可以看到每个循环链路的详细路径，节点颜色代表不同目录，动画箭头指示了依赖方向。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20webpack.config.js%5Cnconst%20CircularDependencyPlugin%20%3D%20require('circular-dependency-plugin')%3B%5Cnconst%20visualizer%20%3D%20require('circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer')%3B%5Cn%5Cnmodule.exports%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%20%20plugins%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20new%20CircularDependencyPlugin(visualizer(%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20exclude%3A%20%2Fnode_modules%2F%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%20HTML%20%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20filepath%3A%20path.join(__dirname%2C%20'circular-deps.html')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D))%5Cn%20%20%5D%5Cn%7D%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22clNbX%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"DHvK8\" id=\"DHvK8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2fdb9ac5\" id=\"u2fdb9ac5\">💡</span><span data-lake-id=\"u5839e14d\" id=\"u5839e14d\"> 总结与建议</span></h3><ol list=\"u3b78526d\"><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"u079042d3\" id=\"u079042d3\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u43dfa9d0\" id=\"u43dfa9d0\">日常开发首选</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua7c317a5\" id=\"ua7c317a5\">：在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8af69b3d\" id=\"u8af69b3d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u189ff285\" id=\"u189ff285\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc3c9e0c9\" id=\"uc3c9e0c9\"> 中引入 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5f767c10\" id=\"u5f767c10\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub8fefe8c\" id=\"ub8fefe8c\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf84cd8e9\" id=\"uf84cd8e9\">，并将其 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u07f645e4\" id=\"u07f645e4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5acada7e\" id=\"u5acada7e\">failOnError</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc42b4243\" id=\"uc42b4243\"> 设置为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1cd881eb\" id=\"u1cd881eb\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba29a43b\" id=\"uba29a43b\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u64a967f9\" id=\"u64a967f9\"> 作为警告，避免打断开发流程，但能时刻提醒你关注。</span></li><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"ub1f6846c\" id=\"ub1f6846c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub55b740c\" id=\"ub55b740c\">代码提交前检查</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u765c8f8d\" id=\"u765c8f8d\">：在 CI/CD 流程或 Git 钩子中，可以运行一个专门的 Webpack 构建，将 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uedc352a7\" id=\"uedc352a7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2f3898c0\" id=\"u2f3898c0\">failOnError</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua480f423\" id=\"ua480f423\"> 设为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uad7bfa80\" id=\"uad7bfa80\"><span data-lake-id=\"u483157d0\" id=\"u483157d0\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9f0f9359\" id=\"u9f0f9359\">，确保任何引入新循环依赖的代码都无法合入。</span></li><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"u2f7677c6\" id=\"u2f7677c6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc1982e3b\" id=\"uc1982e3b\">复杂问题定位</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u124b474f\" id=\"u124b474f\">：当出现难以理解的循环依赖时，使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8eba66ad\" id=\"u8eba66ad\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaacb6bf3\" id=\"uaacb6bf3\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u17fb4d23\" id=\"u17fb4d23\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u245a7bd8\" id=\"u245a7bd8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u02045dc3\" id=\"u02045dc3\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u033197bf\" id=\"u033197bf\"> 生成依赖图，直观地分析模块结构。</span></li><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"u3c71ca8d\" id=\"u3c71ca8d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5ece2d74\" id=\"u5ece2d74\">规范前置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua239cfd0\" id=\"ua239cfd0\">：结合 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udb84e0b0\" id=\"udb84e0b0\">ESLint</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u165ba914\" id=\"u165ba914\"> 规则 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ude5db0d9\" id=\"ude5db0d9\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue8c176a4\" id=\"ue8c176a4\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1b535b68\" id=\"u1b535b68\">，在编码阶段就给开发者最快速的提示。</span></li></ol>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u490e15de\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">检测模块之间的循环依赖，主要可以通过 Webpack 插件、ESLint 规则和可视化工具三种方式来实现。下面为你详细介绍这几种主流方案。</span></p><h3 id=\"vglkn\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🛠️</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 核心方案：使用 Webpack 插件</span></h3><p id=\"u3c578a74\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在 Webpack 构建流程中直接检测和报告循环依赖，是最常用和自动化程度最高的方法。</span></p><h4 id=\"BeRll\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code></h4><p id=\"u8f0f9045\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这是最主流的 Webpack 循环依赖检测插件，每周下载量超过百万，稳定性高。它能在编译时分析模块依赖图，并准确定位循环链路。</span></p><p id=\"u93c11c27\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">安装与基础配置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"JROTR\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code>npm install --save-dev circular-dependency-plugin</code></pre><p id=\"u770814c5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中引入并配置：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"uWEBh\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>const CircularDependencyPlugin = require('circular-dependency-plugin')\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  // ... 其他配置\n  plugins: [\n    new CircularDependencyPlugin({\n      // 排除 node_modules 下的文件\n      exclude: /node_modules/,\n      // 设置为 true 则将循环依赖视为错误，导致构建失败；false 则仅输出警告\n      failOnError: false,\n      // 允许包含异步导入的循环，例如通过 import() 引入\n      allowAsyncCycles: false,\n      // 设置当前工作目录，用于显示模块路径\n      cwd: process.cwd(),\n    })\n  ]\n}</code></pre><p id=\"u0f518fc6\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">进阶用法</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">onDetected</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 钩子，你可以自定义处理逻辑，比如收集所有循环路径并在构建结束时统计数量：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"x8CUC\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>new CircularDependencyPlugin({\n  onDetected({ module: webpackModuleRecord, paths, compilation }) {\n    // paths 是一个包含循环依赖路径的数组，例如 ['a.js', 'b.js', 'a.js']\n    compilation.warnings.push(new Error(paths.join(' -&gt; ')))\n  },\n})</code></pre><h3 id=\"KHjdh\"><span class=\"ne-text\">🔍</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 辅助方案：ESLint 静态检查</span></h3><p id=\"u5ef77fd4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果你希望在编写代码的阶段就能发现循环依赖，可以使用 ESLint 规则。</span></p><h4 id=\"LU7ML\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则</span></h4><p id=\"u258c5d2b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 插件提供的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则，可以在不运行构建的情况下，静态分析代码中的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 语句来检测循环依赖。</span></p><p id=\"u282a5653\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">配置方法</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"json\" id=\"yNma3\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-json\"><code>{\n  &quot;plugins&quot;: [&quot;import&quot;],\n  &quot;rules&quot;: {\n    &quot;import/no-cycle&quot;: [&quot;error&quot;, { &quot;maxDepth&quot;: 10 }]\n  }\n}</code></pre><p id=\"u7d2b732e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这种方式可以让你在开发时实时得到反馈，但它的分析深度和准确性不如在完整构建流程中的 Webpack 插件。</span></p><h3 id=\"GZWfJ\"><span class=\"ne-text\">📊</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 可视化工具：深入理解依赖关系</span></h3><p id=\"uc6345ed9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当项目复杂时，仅仅知道有循环依赖可能还不够，需要直观地看到依赖关系图来帮助重构。</span></p><h4 id=\"fzgVy\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependency-cruiser</span></code></h4><p id=\"u08bf8f98\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 是一个强大的依赖关系分析和可视化工具，可以生成整个项目的依赖关系图，清晰地展示模块间的所有联系，包括循环依赖。</span></p><p id=\"u06053eee\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">基本使用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"ICdHP\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code># 安装\nnpm install --save-dev dependency-cruiser\n\n# 生成依赖图 (SVG 格式)\nnpx depcruise src --include-only &quot;^src&quot; --output-type dot | dot -T svg &gt; dependency-graph.svg</code></pre><h4 id=\"Etujd\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code></h4><p id=\"u5c80da28\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">这个工具可以配合 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 使用，将检测到的循环依赖生成一个交互式的 HTML 可视化页面。页面中，你可以看到每个循环链路的详细路径，节点颜色代表不同目录，动画箭头指示了依赖方向。</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"clNbX\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>// webpack.config.js\nconst CircularDependencyPlugin = require('circular-dependency-plugin');\nconst visualizer = require('circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer');\n\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [\n    new CircularDependencyPlugin(visualizer({\n      exclude: /node_modules/,\n    }, {\n      // 指定输出 HTML 文件的路径\n      filepath: path.join(__dirname, 'circular-deps.html')\n    }))\n  ]\n};</code></pre><h3 id=\"DHvK8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">💡</span><span class=\"ne-text\"> 总结与建议</span></h3><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u079042d3\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">日常开发首选</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中引入 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，并将其 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">failOnError</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 设置为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">false</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 作为警告，避免打断开发流程，但能时刻提醒你关注。</span></li><li id=\"ub1f6846c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">代码提交前检查</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：在 CI/CD 流程或 Git 钩子中，可以运行一个专门的 Webpack 构建，将 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">failOnError</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 设为 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">true</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，确保任何引入新循环依赖的代码都无法合入。</span></li><li id=\"u2f7677c6\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">复杂问题定位</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：当出现难以理解的循环依赖时，使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 生成依赖图，直观地分析模块结构。</span></li><li id=\"u3c71ca8d\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">规范前置</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：结合 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">ESLint</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，在编码阶段就给开发者最快速的提示。</span></li></ol></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u490e15de\" id=\"u490e15de\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5ecaf541\" id=\"u5ecaf541\">检测模块之间的循环依赖，主要可以通过 Webpack 插件、ESLint 规则和可视化工具三种方式来实现。下面为你详细介绍这几种主流方案。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"vglkn\" id=\"vglkn\"><span data-lake-id=\"u346c7c84\" id=\"u346c7c84\">🛠️</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc7566720\" id=\"uc7566720\"> 核心方案：使用 Webpack 插件</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u3c578a74\" id=\"u3c578a74\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub220080d\" id=\"ub220080d\">在 Webpack 构建流程中直接检测和报告循环依赖，是最常用和自动化程度最高的方法。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"BeRll\" id=\"BeRll\"><code data-lake-id=\"ua1810ddd\" id=\"ua1810ddd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u944ea346\" id=\"u944ea346\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u8f0f9045\" id=\"u8f0f9045\"><span data-lake-id=\"u501b6ce5\" id=\"u501b6ce5\">这是最主流的 Webpack 循环依赖检测插件，每周下载量超过百万，稳定性高。它能在编译时分析模块依赖图，并准确定位循环链路。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u93c11c27\" id=\"u93c11c27\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf128ee23\" id=\"uf128ee23\">安装与基础配置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u743f0c94\" id=\"u743f0c94\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22npm%20install%20--save-dev%20circular-dependency-plugin%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22JROTR%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u770814c5\" id=\"u770814c5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5240c42e\" id=\"u5240c42e\">在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3ebfe6de\" id=\"u3ebfe6de\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27a76e2a\" id=\"u27a76e2a\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7237a637\" id=\"u7237a637\"> 中引入并配置：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22const%20CircularDependencyPlugin%20%3D%20require('circular-dependency-plugin')%5Cn%5Cnmodule.exports%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%2F%2F%20...%20%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%5Cn%20%20plugins%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20new%20CircularDependencyPlugin(%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%20node_modules%20%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20exclude%3A%20%2Fnode_modules%2F%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA%20true%20%E5%88%99%E5%B0%86%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E8%A7%86%E4%B8%BA%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%EF%BC%9Bfalse%20%E5%88%99%E4%BB%85%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20failOnError%3A%20false%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%20import()%20%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20allowAsyncCycles%3A%20false%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%8E%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20cwd%3A%20process.cwd()%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D)%5Cn%20%20%5D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22uWEBh%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u0f518fc6\" id=\"u0f518fc6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u13990860\" id=\"u13990860\">进阶用法</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3af10ac4\" id=\"u3af10ac4\">：通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u95826e35\" id=\"u95826e35\"><span data-lake-id=\"u068d9c3a\" id=\"u068d9c3a\">onDetected</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3da17c1d\" id=\"u3da17c1d\"> 钩子，你可以自定义处理逻辑，比如收集所有循环路径并在构建结束时统计数量：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22new%20CircularDependencyPlugin(%7B%5Cn%20%20onDetected(%7B%20module%3A%20webpackModuleRecord%2C%20paths%2C%20compilation%20%7D)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20paths%20%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8C%85%E5%90%AB%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%20%5B'a.js'%2C%20'b.js'%2C%20'a.js'%5D%5Cn%20%20%20%20compilation.warnings.push(new%20Error(paths.join('%20-%3E%20')))%5Cn%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22x8CUC%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"KHjdh\" id=\"KHjdh\"><span data-lake-id=\"uff312419\" id=\"uff312419\">🔍</span><span data-lake-id=\"u06c1e3e9\" id=\"u06c1e3e9\"> 辅助方案：ESLint 静态检查</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u5ef77fd4\" id=\"u5ef77fd4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1c0e7753\" id=\"u1c0e7753\">如果你希望在编写代码的阶段就能发现循环依赖，可以使用 ESLint 规则。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"LU7ML\" id=\"LU7ML\"><code data-lake-id=\"u49fa1b72\" id=\"u49fa1b72\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4068a601\" id=\"u4068a601\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uecc8ca56\" id=\"uecc8ca56\"> 规则</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u258c5d2b\" id=\"u258c5d2b\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufd19a840\" id=\"ufd19a840\">通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufeea798b\" id=\"ufeea798b\"><span data-lake-id=\"udc84f058\" id=\"udc84f058\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udb767fbf\" id=\"udb767fbf\"> 插件提供的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf1d2616a\" id=\"uf1d2616a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u03b43b8a\" id=\"u03b43b8a\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u03947040\" id=\"u03947040\"> 规则，可以在不运行构建的情况下，静态分析代码中的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud96cf7d1\" id=\"ud96cf7d1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u92158cd8\" id=\"u92158cd8\">import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u43a8242a\" id=\"u43a8242a\"> 语句来检测循环依赖。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u282a5653\" id=\"u282a5653\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u080b39e4\" id=\"u080b39e4\">配置方法</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u23681dd9\" id=\"u23681dd9\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22json%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%7B%5Cn%20%20%5C%22plugins%5C%22%3A%20%5B%5C%22import%5C%22%5D%2C%5Cn%20%20%5C%22rules%5C%22%3A%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5C%22import%2Fno-cycle%5C%22%3A%20%5B%5C%22error%5C%22%2C%20%7B%20%5C%22maxDepth%5C%22%3A%2010%20%7D%5D%5Cn%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22yNma3%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u7d2b732e\" id=\"u7d2b732e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufc391d93\" id=\"ufc391d93\">这种方式可以让你在开发时实时得到反馈，但它的分析深度和准确性不如在完整构建流程中的 Webpack 插件。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"GZWfJ\" id=\"GZWfJ\"><span data-lake-id=\"uddd27698\" id=\"uddd27698\">📊</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc119ca2c\" id=\"uc119ca2c\"> 可视化工具：深入理解依赖关系</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"uc6345ed9\" id=\"uc6345ed9\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf4a70df0\" id=\"uf4a70df0\">当项目复杂时，仅仅知道有循环依赖可能还不够，需要直观地看到依赖关系图来帮助重构。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id=\"fzgVy\" id=\"fzgVy\"><code data-lake-id=\"u96691362\" id=\"u96691362\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub4040051\" id=\"ub4040051\">dependency-cruiser</span></code></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u08bf8f98\" id=\"u08bf8f98\"><code data-lake-id=\"u814c1a53\" id=\"u814c1a53\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8e492ef5\" id=\"u8e492ef5\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u29f514dc\" id=\"u29f514dc\"> 是一个强大的依赖关系分析和可视化工具，可以生成整个项目的依赖关系图，清晰地展示模块间的所有联系，包括循环依赖。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u06053eee\" id=\"u06053eee\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u61e4022a\" id=\"u61e4022a\">基本使用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua07a563e\" id=\"ua07a563e\">：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%5Cnnpm%20install%20--save-dev%20dependency-cruiser%5Cn%5Cn%23%20%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E5%9B%BE%20(SVG%20%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F)%5Cnnpx%20depcruise%20src%20--include-only%20%5C%22%5Esrc%5C%22%20--output-type%20dot%20%7C%20dot%20-T%20svg%20%3E%20dependency-graph.svg%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22ICdHP%22%7D\"></card><h4 data-lake-id=\"Etujd\" id=\"Etujd\"><code data-lake-id=\"ub81511eb\" id=\"ub81511eb\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a8a5516\" id=\"u3a8a5516\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u5c80da28\" id=\"u5c80da28\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a15cf0c\" id=\"u7a15cf0c\">这个工具可以配合 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1aa18db\" id=\"ua1aa18db\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud08fa4bf\" id=\"ud08fa4bf\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3d633b0d\" id=\"u3d633b0d\"> 使用，将检测到的循环依赖生成一个交互式的 HTML 可视化页面。页面中，你可以看到每个循环链路的详细路径，节点颜色代表不同目录，动画箭头指示了依赖方向。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20webpack.config.js%5Cnconst%20CircularDependencyPlugin%20%3D%20require('circular-dependency-plugin')%3B%5Cnconst%20visualizer%20%3D%20require('circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer')%3B%5Cn%5Cnmodule.exports%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%20%20plugins%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20new%20CircularDependencyPlugin(visualizer(%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20exclude%3A%20%2Fnode_modules%2F%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%20HTML%20%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20filepath%3A%20path.join(__dirname%2C%20'circular-deps.html')%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D))%5Cn%20%20%5D%5Cn%7D%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22clNbX%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"DHvK8\" id=\"DHvK8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2fdb9ac5\" id=\"u2fdb9ac5\">💡</span><span data-lake-id=\"u5839e14d\" id=\"u5839e14d\"> 总结与建议</span></h3><ol list=\"u3b78526d\"><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"u079042d3\" id=\"u079042d3\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u43dfa9d0\" id=\"u43dfa9d0\">日常开发首选</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua7c317a5\" id=\"ua7c317a5\">：在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8af69b3d\" id=\"u8af69b3d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u189ff285\" id=\"u189ff285\">webpack.config.js</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc3c9e0c9\" id=\"uc3c9e0c9\"> 中引入 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u5f767c10\" id=\"u5f767c10\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub8fefe8c\" id=\"ub8fefe8c\">circular-dependency-plugin</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf84cd8e9\" id=\"uf84cd8e9\">，并将其 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u07f645e4\" id=\"u07f645e4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5acada7e\" id=\"u5acada7e\">failOnError</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc42b4243\" id=\"uc42b4243\"> 设置为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1cd881eb\" id=\"u1cd881eb\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba29a43b\" id=\"uba29a43b\">false</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u64a967f9\" id=\"u64a967f9\"> 作为警告，避免打断开发流程，但能时刻提醒你关注。</span></li><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"ub1f6846c\" id=\"ub1f6846c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub55b740c\" id=\"ub55b740c\">代码提交前检查</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u765c8f8d\" id=\"u765c8f8d\">：在 CI/CD 流程或 Git 钩子中，可以运行一个专门的 Webpack 构建，将 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uedc352a7\" id=\"uedc352a7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2f3898c0\" id=\"u2f3898c0\">failOnError</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua480f423\" id=\"ua480f423\"> 设为 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uad7bfa80\" id=\"uad7bfa80\"><span data-lake-id=\"u483157d0\" id=\"u483157d0\">true</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u9f0f9359\" id=\"u9f0f9359\">，确保任何引入新循环依赖的代码都无法合入。</span></li><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"u2f7677c6\" id=\"u2f7677c6\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc1982e3b\" id=\"uc1982e3b\">复杂问题定位</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u124b474f\" id=\"u124b474f\">：当出现难以理解的循环依赖时，使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u8eba66ad\" id=\"u8eba66ad\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaacb6bf3\" id=\"uaacb6bf3\">dependency-cruiser</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u17fb4d23\" id=\"u17fb4d23\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u245a7bd8\" id=\"u245a7bd8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u02045dc3\" id=\"u02045dc3\">circular-dependency-plugin-visualizer</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u033197bf\" id=\"u033197bf\"> 生成依赖图，直观地分析模块结构。</span></li><li fid=\"u56eb08bd\" data-lake-id=\"u3c71ca8d\" id=\"u3c71ca8d\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5ece2d74\" id=\"u5ece2d74\">规范前置</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua239cfd0\" id=\"ua239cfd0\">：结合 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udb84e0b0\" id=\"udb84e0b0\">ESLint</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u165ba914\" id=\"u165ba914\"> 规则 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ude5db0d9\" id=\"ude5db0d9\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue8c176a4\" id=\"ue8c176a4\">import/no-cycle</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1b535b68\" id=\"u1b535b68\">，在编码阶段就给开发者最快速的提示。</span></li></ol>","word_count":965,"slug":"tewhnng4yf4ynt0y","type":"Doc","title":"如何检测模块之间的循环依赖？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"检测模块之间的循环依赖，主要可以通过 Webpack 插件、ESLint 规则和可视化工具三种方式来实现。下面为你详细介绍这几种主流方案。🛠️ 核心方案：使用 Webpack 插件在 Webpack 构建流程中直接检测和报告循环依赖，是最常用和自动化程度最高的方法。circular-depe...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"codeblock\":6}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-28T07:28:03.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-28T07:28:50.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-28T07:28:50.189Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-28T07:28:50.000Z","id":258574913},"doc_digest":"_h9_v7YbrDSEIoJnrZOqGPKoMlU"}